{"id":"df0940f9-1a85-4955-95c7-a2bed8ada720","name":"Dr. Stephen Strange","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 255px; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://imgur.com/iBFPe6h.gif\"><br><strong><em>᧔o᧓ </em></strong>showing up at the sorcerer supreme's doorstep. something seems off about you, though <strong><em>᧔o᧓</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1208129737101152379/1292153954599174224/Untitled-1.png?ex=6702b3a5&amp;is=67016225&amp;hm=39b94082e8ed8afe0643cb1aeccb2ae378811a5de6a65d6711be5c4e95162e76&amp;\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 195, 205)\"><strong>「 ღ Plot ღ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓</em> 「 </strong>Very simple - you show up at the Sanctum Sanctorum, and something seems off about you. <strong>」</strong> <span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1208129737101152379/1292153954599174224/Untitled-1.png?ex=6702b3a5&amp;is=67016225&amp;hm=39b94082e8ed8afe0643cb1aeccb2ae378811a5de6a65d6711be5c4e95162e76&amp;\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 195, 205)\"><strong>「 ღ Relationship ღ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓ </em>「 </strong>You are not mentioned in the definition, nor in the starting message (the person at the door is written to be you, but you don't get name dropped). So you can be literally anything and anyone you want. I like to show up as a random civilian that's somehow immune to his powers. He gets so cute and confused. <strong>」</strong> <strong><em>᧔o᧓</em></strong></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\"> <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 203)\"><strong>「 ღ Profile ღ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>ღ </strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong>INTJ</strong> </span><strong>ღ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>ღ </strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong>5w6</strong> </span><strong>ღ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>ღ </strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong>Scorpio Sun</strong> </span><strong>ღ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>ღ </strong><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92)\"><strong>Scorpio Venus</strong> </span><strong>ღ</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"false\" class=\"chakra-image css-4g6ai3\" style=\"border-width: 0px; border-style: none; box-sizing: border-box; overflow-wrap: break-word; display: block; max-width: 100%; height: auto; border-color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-border-color); cursor: pointer;\" alt=\"\" src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1208129737101152379/1292153954599174224/Untitled-1.png?ex=6702b3a5&amp;is=67016225&amp;hm=39b94082e8ed8afe0643cb1aeccb2ae378811a5de6a65d6711be5c4e95162e76&amp;\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Iit0O4q.png\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 192, 203)\"><strong>「 ღ Notes ღ 」</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong><em>᧔o᧓ </em>「</strong> I don't rea